{"comments":"Canvas2D Rendering Target\n\nRenders DrawCommands to a 2D canvas context. This is the most compatible\nGPU target, working on essentially all browsers including:\n- All mobile browsers (iOS Safari, Android Chrome/Firefox)\n- All desktop browsers\n- Node.js with node-canvas\n\n## Performance Characteristics\n\nCanvas2D is CPU-rendered but hardware-accelerated for compositing.\nGood for:\n- Simple 2D graphics\n- < 1000 draw calls per frame\n- Broad compatibility requirements\n\nNot ideal for:\n- > 10,000 particles (use WebGL/WebGPU)\n- Complex shaders\n- 3D rendering\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Target.Canvas2D as Canvas2D\nimport Hydrogen.GPU.Flatten as Flatten\n\nrenderToCanvas :: Element Msg -> Effect Unit\nrenderToCanvas element = do\n  ctx <- Canvas2D.getContext2D \"my-canvas\"\n  let result = Flatten.flatten element\n  Canvas2D.render ctx result.commands\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Opaque 2D canvas rendering context.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"data","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[118,38],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Target/Canvas2D.purs","start":[118,1]},"title":"Context2D"},{"children":[],"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Target","Canvas2D"],"Context2D"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Effect"],"Effect"],"tag":"TypeCo